          "action": "Put both flours into a separate bowl with the baking powder, bicarbonate of soda, and \u00be teaspoon of salt. Whisk to combine and aerate, then add the grated beetroot and all but 1 tablespoon of the oat and seed mix. Don\u2019t stir the mixture: just set it aside.",
